        "print(\"\"\"\n",
        "Section 3 - Heartbeat Detection and Segmentation\n",
        "======================================================================\n",
        "\n",
        "Rather than reinventing R-peak detection from scratch, we use the expert\n",
        "cardiologist annotations included with MIT-BIH (the clinical gold standard)\n",
        "to locate each heartbeat precisely. This mirrors how real algorithm validation\n",
        "works: an automated detector's output is compared against these same\n",
        "expert-labeled annotations.\n",
        "\n",
        "For each annotated beat, we extract a fixed-size window around the R-peak,\n",
        "giving us a segmented \"heartbeat\" ready for feature extraction.\n",
        "\"\"\")"
      ],
